{"tid":646253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"卓林去年計劃出自傳　內容涉及成龍","createTime":"2018-04-29T01:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T02:14:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"15c720c85d7240cc471405443f73b7f92a67422d","tid":646253,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:24:40.000Z","msg":"卓林突然公開拍片，疑似受人擺佈，但其實她一直有很多心底話想分享。去年3月，她報警指母親涉嫌刑事恐嚇時，本報曾嘗試聯絡她做專訪，當時她表示會考慮，並透露打算推出一本自傳，內容涉及生父成龍，不過她與Andi商量一晚後婉拒。<br />\n<br />\n自傳講成龍<br />\n作為吳綺莉的好友郭秀雲，對於卓林與Andi的「求助片」，昨日她回覆本報時爆料，指Andi母親曾向吳綺莉索生活費：「我知道嗰個補習老師個媽媽，曾經叫吳綺莉send個女去加拿大，去佢嗰度住，話求其收番佢幾萬蚊一個月，都唔係細銀碼。如果個阿媽喺加拿大，可以照顧到，咁點解佢哋要搞到話要淪落街頭呢？再加上望落佢兩個都肥肥白白，似乎拍嘢嗰度，背景係屋企。」對於郭秀雲指她被Andi母親索生活費一事，吳綺莉昨日透過電話以一個無奈的emoji作回覆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180429/large/29ec1p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180429%2Flarge%2F29ec1p6.jpg&h=6c2ca54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180429/20376036\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180429%2F20376036&d=rkM8dvoGC4zeQMu%2F0UsLqSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=868380d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180429%2F20376036&h=59e8319c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180429/20376036</a>"},{"pid":"d86f8a3348dc4871228b8e9e6703719a8d3f3854","tid":646253,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:25:28.000Z","msg":"得啦知啦"},{"pid":"57b3ac1f758e5dba782d165942757dfce2f5b093","tid":646253,"uid":31920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"都無人想知<br />\n<br />\n記者朋友收完鱔稿費就好收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" 